125
00:06:46,810 --> 00:06:48,030
Alright, I understand.

126
00:06:48,380 --> 00:06:49,300
Then I'll head over now.

127
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:56,150
What's wrong?

128
00:06:59,420 --> 00:07:00,570
The school's student council

129
00:07:00,620 --> 00:07:01,950
