224
00:12:14,860 --> 00:12:16,390
It's okay, it's okay. Mommy will buy you one.

225
00:12:17,490 --> 00:12:18,200
It's alright.

226
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:19,250
I'm sorry.

227
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:20,490
It's okay, it's okay. Don't worry.

228
