If I finish early, I'll come back to you.

229
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:33,670
I'm really sorry about this.

230
00:12:33,690 --> 00:12:34,770
Bye-bye, bye-bye.

231
00:12:35,250 --> 00:12:35,690
