268
00:14:38,700 --> 00:14:40,250
But I have to look after the Vice President of the Comic Club.

269
00:14:42,310 --> 00:14:42,920
Who?

270
00:14:44,640 --> 00:14:45,210
You.

271
00:14:48,170 --> 00:14:50,140
